1 N1 'dul ba, ka 1b1-nga 470a7 (vol. 1-4) 17 chapters 'dul ba gzhi - 'dul ba'i gzhi rdzogs s+Ho/ /kha che'i mkhan po sarba dz+nyA de ba dang / rgya gar gyi mkhan po bid+yA ka ra pra b+ha dang / kha che'i mkhan po d+ha rmA ka ra dang / lo ts+tsha ba ban de dpal gyi lhun pos bsgyur/ rgya gar gyi mkhan po bid+yA ka ra pra b+ha dang / zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban de dpal brtsegs kyis zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
2 N2 'dul ba, ca 1b1-30b1 (vol. 5) dge slong pha'i so thar - so sor thar pa'i mdo rdzogs s+ho// 'phags pa gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba 'dzin pa/ kha che bye brag tu smra ba'i slob dpon dzi na mi tra dang / zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he cog gru klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
3 N3 'dul ba, ca 30b2-nya 471a6 (vol. 5-8) 'dul ba rnam par 'byed pa - 'dul ba rnam par 'byed pa rdzogs so/ /dbang phyug dam pa'i mnga' bdag dpal lha btsan po'i bka' lung gis/ 'phags pa gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba 'dzin pa kha che'i bye brag tu smra ba'i slob dpon dzi na mi tra dang / zhu chen gyi lo tsa ba ban de klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa/ 'di la sho lo ka ni nyi khri lnga stong yod/ bam po brgyad cu rtsa gsum du byas so/ /'dul ba rnam par 'byed pa rdzogs so//
4 N4 'dul ba, ta 1b1-36b5 (vol. 9) dge slong ma'i so thar - dge slong ma'i so sor thar pa'i mdo rdzogs so/ /dbang phyug dam pa'i mnga' bdag /dpal lha btsan po'i bka' lung gis 'phags pa gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba 'dzin pa kha che bye brag tu smra ba'i slob dpon dzi na mi tra dang /zhu chen gyi lots+tsha ba cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa/
5 N5 'dul ba, ta 36b6-483 (vol. 9) dge slong ma'i 'dul ba rnam par 'byed pa - dge slong ma'i 'dul ba rnam par 'byed pa/ so sor thar pa dang bcas pa rdzogs so/ /kha che'i mkhan po sarba dz+nyA de ba dang / d+harma ka ra dang / rgya gar gyi mkhan po bid+yA ka ra pra b+ha dang / lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he dpal gyi lhun pos bsgyur/ rgya gar gyi mkhan po bid+yA ka ra pra b+ha dang / zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he dpal brtsegs kyis zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
6 N6 'dul ba, tha 1b1-da 708a4 (vol. 10-11) 'dul ba phran tshegs kyi gzhi - 'dul ba phran tshegs kyi gzhi rdzogs so/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po bid+ya ka ra pra b+ha dang / d+harma shrI pra b+ha dang / lo tsa ba ban d+he dpal 'byor gyis bsgyur/ zhus dag legs par byas so/ /phran tshegs 'di la dpe mang yang / /yid bstan thub pa cig kyang med/ /'gyur yang cung zad mi bde zhing / /tshig brul brda rnying mngas pa dang/ /glegs bam tha mar nye ba yis/ zhu dag mkhan po rnams kyis kyang / /sems dub skyo ba'i dbang gis ni/ /phal cher btang snyoms bzhag par mngon/ /klag mi bde zhing brir mi bde/ /cung zad bcos su 'ang mi bde zhing/ /thams cad the tshom gzhir gyur pas/ /kho bo'i sems kyang cung zad dub/ /'on kyang brnag par ma dor bar/ /spro dang 'dun pa'i sems kyis ni/ /dam pa'i thugs dgongs mthar phyin cing / /bstan pa'i rgyun la 'ang phan bsams nas/ /dus ni cung zad 'gor na yang / /long med rings tshul ma byas par/ /'ol tshod rang bzo spangs nas ni/ /legs brtags legs par rab dpyad nas/ /shin tu nges pa'i tshul gyis ni/ /the tsom za rnams zer mtshan bkod/ /gdon mi za rnams legs par bcos/ /tshul 'di mkhas pa'i gtsug rgyan du/ /phyi mtha' bar du 'gyur bar shog /'di ni phyi mo la gtugs pa dang snar thang gi dpe la gtugs pa'i zhus dag gnyis kyi rjes la sog tshul khrims bla ma'i phyag dpe la gtugs pa'i zhus dag nan can lan gnyis te bzhi tshar ba'i rjes su/ slob dpon tshul khrims bskyangs kyi 'grel pa dang stun cing / mdo rtsa'i 'grel chen rnams su lung dngas pa dang yang sgrigs/ cho ga rnams las brgya rtsa cig gi gzhung dang yang bstun/ tshig 'dra la 'dra min rnams kyang / don la legs par dpyad nas dag par byas/ 'di la da rung chad pa 'ga' re yod pas rgya dpe rnyed na gtug dgos so/ /thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo/ /sngon bstan pa snga dar la lung phran tshegs kyi gzhi 'di bsgyur ba'i dus su lo ts+tsha ba du mas dum bu mang por bgos te so sor tha dad du bsgyur bas glegs bam gcig tu sdom pa'i tshe na/ gnas gcig tu ma tshang par bsdebs shing / lo tsh+tsha ba chen po dpal 'byor gyis rdzogs par zhu chen ma grub pas/ 'khrug chad can du phran tshegs phal cher bzhugs pa las/ dus phyis gnas brtan dar ma seng ges/ la stod 'ol rgod kyi gtsug lag khang du lung sde bzhi bzhengs pa'i tshe/ zhing mo che pa 'dul 'dzin byang chub seng ges dbus rtsang gi gtsug lang khang dang / khyad par bsam yas mchims phu na dgas chung ba dang tshul khrims yon tan gyis rnyed pa'i lung dag pa la dpe yon phul nas 'bad pas dag par bgyis pa la/ bam po sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i mgor sman chen po'i gtam gyi skabs su/ sman chen pos smras pa/ gal te de lta na skyugs shig dang bden nam brdzun blta'o zhes pa nas/ bam po sum cu rtsa bzhi pa'i dbur/ ji tsam grong khyer nas byung ba dang bram ze mong rtul zhes bya bas gos kyi mtha' nas 'jus zhes pa'i bar bam po gcig bsabs/ sdom ni/ nga yang sman gyis de bzhin no/ /zhes pa'i 'og tu yig tshar gcig bskangs/ bam po sum cu rtsa bzhi pa'i smad ne tsho spyod gsal gyi skabs rdzogs par e ma'o 'di ltar khyod mkhas pa sha stag dang phrad pa ni bsod nams dang ldan no zhes pa nas/ bam po bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi pa'i stod du spyi'i sdom ni/dge slong ma'i bkur bsti bri/ zhes pa'i bar bam po dgu chad pa bsabs/ de'i 'og tu sdom tshig yig tshar gcig chad pa bskangs/ bam po bzhi bcu rtsabaduna pa'i 'jug bram ze'i khye'u ma sdug gi gtam 'phror/ dge sbyong rnams kyi yon po'i spyad kyi log pa'i 'tsho ba de lta bu las slar log pa yin no/ /nas bam po bzhi bcu rtsa dgu pa'i dbur/ de'i tshe bram ze pad ma'i snying po khyim mchog gis mthon po zhig na shas che ba'i bram ze rgan rabs rnams dang lhan cig 'dus shing 'khod do zhes pa'i bar bam po bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad pa bsabs/ de nas bam po nga gcig pa'i 'jug kun daga'o la gdams par chos kyi skyabs kyi gnas par bya'i/ gling gzhan dang skyabs gzhan gyis ni ma yin no nas/ bam po nga gsum pa'i stod du/ bar sdom ni/ tsa pa la dang tshe'i 'du byed mdzad kyi bar bam bo gcig bskangs te/ dag par bzhengs pa'i lung de la phyi mo mdzad nas/ snar thang du mkhan chen mchims nam mkha' grags kyis dag par bzhengs pa'i dpe la gtugs zhus dag bgyi'o/ /lo rgyus 'di lung phran tshegs kyi glegs bam la shin tu gces pas/
7 N7 'dul ba, na 1b1-139a3 (vol. 12) 'dul ba gzhung bla ma -
739 N8 'dul ba, na 139a3-458a6 (vol. 12) 'dul ba gzhung dam pa - 'dul ba gzhung dam pa rdzogs te/ u pa lis kun dris pa rdzogs so//
8 N9 'bum, ka 1b1-na 536a5 (vol. 14-25) shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag brgya pa - rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang/ su ren+dra bo de dang / zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban+de ye shes sde la sogs pas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o/ /zhus dag
9 N10 nyi khri, ka 1b1-ga 543a7 (vol. 26-28) shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa - shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa/ phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi 'das pa dang/ ma byon pa dang / da ltar gyi sangs rgyas dang/ byang chub sems dpa' dang / nyan thos dang/ rang sangs rgyas rnams kyi yum rdzogs so//zhus dag
10 N11 khri brgyad, ka 1b1-ga 213a4 (vol. 29-31) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa khri brgyad stong pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo -
11 N12 khri pa, ka 1b1-613a7 (vol. 32) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa khri pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa khri pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang/ pra dz+nyA warma dang/ zhu chen gyi lo tsA ba ban+de ye shes sdes zhus te gtan la phab pa
12 N13 brgyad stong, ka 1b1-462a2 (vol. 33) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa - bcom ldan 'das ma 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa rdzogs s+ho/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po shAkya se na dang dz+nyA na sid d+hi dang/ zhu chen gyi lo tsA ba ban+de.e d+harma tA shI la la sogs pas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab/ slad kyis dbang phyug dam pa'i mnga' bdag bod kyi dpal lha btsan po bkra shis lha lde btsan gyi bkas/ rgya gar gyi mkhan po su b+hA Shi ta dang/ sgra bsgyur gyi lo tsA ba dge slong rin chen bzang pos 'grel pa dang mthun par bsgyur/ slad kyis rgya gar gyi mkhan po paN+Di ta chen po dI paM ka ra shrI dz+nyA na dang / zhu chen gyi lo tsA ba dge slong rin chen bzang pos yul dbus kyi 'grel pa la gtugs nas bcos shing zhus te gtan la phab/ yang slad kyis skyid smad gnye thang na mo cher/ paN+Di ta chen po dI paM ka ra shrI dz+nyA na dang / lo tsA ba 'brom rgyal ba'i 'byung gnas gnyis kyis brgyad stong pa bshad pa'i dus su che long zhig gtan la phab/ phyis rwa sgreng gi gtsug lag khang du lo tsA ba 'brom rgyal ba'i 'byung gnas kyis rgya gar gyi mdo gsum la gtugs nas lan gnyis gtan la phab/ slad kyis yang lo tsA ba de nyid kyis bshad pa mdzad cing phran tshegs kyang gtan la phab/ dus phyis lo tsA ba chen po shAkya'i dge slong blo ldan shes rab kyis kha che'i dpe dang yul dbus kyi dpe du ma bsags nas gtan la phab/ slar yang snyigs dus kyi thams cad mkhyen pa chen po/ zha lu lo tsA ba dpal rin chen chos skyong bzang po'i zhal snga nas kyis/ rgya bod kyi dpe du ma dang bstun nas shin tu rnam par dag par mdzad pa'i ma phyi las slar yang zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//zhus dag
14 N14 sna tshogs, ka 1b1-130a5 (vol. 34) rab rtsal rnam gnon gyis zhus pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi rtsal gyis rnam par gnon pas zhus pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bstan pa rdzogs so
24 N15 sna tshogs, ka 130a5-169b7 (vol. 34) sher phyin gras bdun brgya pa / shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bdun brgya pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bdun brgya pa rdzogs so
15 N16 sna tshogs, ka 169b7-196b5 (vol. 34) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lnga brgya pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lnga brgya pa rdzogs so
13 N17 sna tshogs, ka 196b6-222a5 (vol. 34) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sdud pa tshigs su bcad pa - shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sdud pa tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs s+ho
16 N18 sna tshogs, ka 222a6-240a3 (vol. 34) rdo rje gcod pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rdo rje gcod pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs s+ho
17 N19 sna tshogs, ka 240a3-249b7 (vol. 34) sher phyin tshul brgya lnga bcu pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul brgya lnga bcu pa rdzogs so
25 N20 sna tshogs, ka 250a1-252a6 (vol. 34) sher phyin mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa rdzogs s+ho
18 N21 sna tshogs, ka 252a7-255b4 (vol. 34) 'phags pa bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lnga bcu pa - shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lnga bcu pa rdzogs s+ho
23 N22 sna tshogs, ka 255b4-256a3 (vol. 34) sher phyin yi ge gsig ma - shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yi ge gcig ma rdzogs s+ho
19 N23 sna tshogs, ka 256a3-258a7 (vol. 34) sher phyin ko'u shi ga - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ko'u shi ka zhes bya ba rdzogs s+ho
22 N24 sna tshogs, ka 258b1-261a1 (vol. 34) sher phyin yi ge nyung ngu - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yi ge nyung ngu zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so
490 N25 sna tshogs, ka 261a1-262b1 (vol. 34) sher phyin sgo nyer lnga pa - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgo nyi shu rtsa lnga pa zhes bya ba/ theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs s+ho
529 N26 sna tshogs, ka 262b1-264a4 (vol. 34) bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i snying po - 'phags pa bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i snying po rdzogs s+ho
26 N27 sna tshogs, ka 264a4-266a3 (vol. 34) sher phyin nyi ma'i sning po - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa nyi ma'i snying po theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs s+ho
27 N28 sna tshogs, ka 266a3-267b4 (vol. 34) sher phyin zla ba'i snyng po - 'phags pa zla ba'i snying po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs s+ho
28 N29 sna tshogs, ka 267b4-268b1 (vol. 34) sher phyin kun tu bzang po - 'phags pa kun tu bzang po theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs s+ho
29 N30 sna tshogs, ka 268b1-269a5 (vol. 34) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lag na rdo rje'i mdo theg pa chen po - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa lag na rdo rje'i mdo theg pa chen po rdzogs so
30 N31 sna tshogs, ka 269a5-270 (vol. 34) 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi mdo theg pa chen po - 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi mdo rdzogs s+ho
45 N32 dkon brtsegs, ka 1b1-84a7 (vol. 35) sdom pa gsum bstan pa'i le'u zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/ sdom pa gsum bstan pa zhes bya ba'i le'u dang po rdzogs so//rgya gar gyi mkhan po 'dzi na mi tra dang/ su ren dra bo d+hi dang/ zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te skad gsar bcad kyis gtan la phab pa/ /sho lo ka dgu brgya ste bam po gsum pa'o
46 N33 dkon brtsegs, ka 84b1-171b2 (vol. 35) 'phags pa sgo mtha' yas pa rnam par sbyong ba bstan pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/ sgo mtha' yas pa rnam par sbyong ba bstan pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste/ sho lo ka stong nyis brgya ste bam po bzhi pa'o/ /'dus pa gnyis pa rdzogs so
47 N34 dkon brtsegs, ka 171b2-341b6 (vol. 35) 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/ de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste/ gsum pa rdzogs so/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang/ dA na shI la dang/ mu ne war ma dang/ zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te/ skad gsar bcad kyis kyang gtan la phab pa/ sho lo ka sum stong/ bam po bcu'o
48 N35 dkon brtsegs, ka 341b6-394a7 (vol. 35) 'phags pa rmi lam brtan pa - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs stong phrag brgya pa las/ rmi lam bstan pa'i le'u zhes bya ba ste/ 'dus pa bzhi pa rdzogs so/ /sho lo ka dgu brgya/ bam po gsum pa/ rgya gar gyi mkhan po pradz+nyA bar ma dang/ zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he ye shes sde la sogs pas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa
49 N36 dkon brtsegs, ka 394a7-448a5 (vol. 35) 'phags pa 'od dpag med kyi zhing gi bkod pa - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs stong phrag brgya pa las/ de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi bkod pa'i le'u zhes bya ste/ le'u lnga pa rdzogs so/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po 'dzi na mi tra dang/ dA na shI la dang/ zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba ban d+he ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te/ skad gsar bcad kyis kyang bcos nas gtan la phab pa/ sho lo k+ka dgu brgya ste bam po gsum mo
50 N37 dkon brtsegs, kha 1b1-112a1 (vol. 36) 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa mi 'khrugs pa'i bkod pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/ mi 'khrugs pa'i bkod pa'i le'u zhes bya ba ste drug pa rdzogs so/ /shwa lo ka stong lnga brgya bzhi bcu ste/ bam po lnga'o/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang / su ren dra bo d+hi dang / zhu chen gyi lo tsa ba ban de ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o
51 N38 dkon brtsegs, kha 112a2-219b1 (vol. 36) 'phags pa go cha'i bkod pa bstan pa'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/go cha'i bkod pa bstan pa'i 'dus pa ste/ 'dus pa bdun pa rdzogs s+ho/ /lo ts+tsha ba mgos chos grub kyis rgya'i dpe las bsgyur ba'o
52 N39 dkon brtsegs, kha 219b1-255a4 (vol. 36) 'phags pa chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin dbyer med par bstan pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs stong phrag brgya pa las/ chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin dbyer med par bstan pa'i le'u ste/ brgyad pa rdzogs so/ /shwa lo ka drug brgya lnga bcu/ bam po gnyis so
53 N40 dkon brtsegs, kha 255a4-286b7 (vol. 36) 'phags pa chos bcu pa'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/ chos bcu pa'i le'u ste/ dgu pa rdzogs so/ /sho lo ka lnga brgya sum bcu mchis te/ bam po gnyis so/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang / su ren dra bo d+hi dang / zhu chen gyi lo tsa ba ban d+he ye shes sde la sogs pas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa
54 N41 dkon brtsegs, kha 287a1-304a4 (vol. 36) 'phags pa kun nas sgo'i le'u - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs stong phrag brgya pa las/ kun nas sgo'i le'u zhes bya ba ste le'u bcu pa rdzogs so/ /shwa lo ka nyis brgya drug bcu'o/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang / su ren dra bo d+hi dang / zhu chen gyi lo tsha ba ban de ye shes sdes zhus te gtan la phab pa
55 N42 dkon brtsegs, kha 304a4-402a5 (vol. 36) 'phags pa 'od zer kun nas bkye ba bstan pa - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po chos kyi rnam grangs le'u stong phrag brgya pa las/ 'od zer rab tu bkye ba'i le'u ste 'dus pa bcu gcig pa rdzogs s+ho/ /sho lo ka stong lnga brgya pa/ bam po lnga'o
56 N43 dkon brtsegs, ga 1b1-408a1 (vol. 37) 'phags pa byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod ces bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo - 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs stong phrag brgya pa las/ 'phags pa byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod ces bya ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs kyi le'u ste/ 'dus pa bcu gnyis pa rdzogs s+ho/ /'di la sho lo ka stong phrag drug bam po nyi shu yod do/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po su ren dra bo d+hi dang / shI lan dra bo d+hi dang / lo tsha ba chen po zhang d+harma tA shI las bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa
